<HEADLINE> Thailand Lodges Protest on Cambodian Shelling </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BANGKOK, August 28 (Xinhua) -- The Thai Foreign Ministry today
lodged a protest against Cambodia's shelling on the Thai territory
Tuesday, which killed one Thai soldier and injured two others.
</P>
