a town commanding a corridor that joins halves of the Bosnian Serb
enclave.
</P>
<P>
-- Israel lifted its blockade of Bethlehem, imposed after last
month's Jerusalem bombings and maintained after restrictions on
travel between other West Bank towns had been eased. 
