States, Britain, Canada, New Zealand and Singapore. Two
universities in China's inland areas have also been invited to
join.
</P>
<P>
One of the goals of Universitas 21 is to develop an
international quality assurance structure, the report said.
</P>
<P>
Universitas 21 members will cooperate on curriculum development
and exchange of academics. Member universities will take turns
hosting an annual conference with the University of Melbourne
holding the secretariat until 2000.  
