<HEADLINE> NZ Stocks Finish Higher </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
WELLINGTON, August 28 (Xinhua) -- The New Zealand share market
rose today in thin trading as investors kept a wary eye on Wall
Street despite its positive close overnight after four days of
losses.
</P>
<P>
