<HEADLINE> New Zealand Praised for Peace Role for PNG </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
WELLINGTON, August 28 (Xinhua) -- New Zealand's initiative in
hosting talks for peace on Papua New Guinea's Bougainville Island
has won widespread praise in PNG where Foreign Minister Don
MaKinnon is paying a visit.
</P>
