increased by 212 in the first half to 535. The United States,
Germany, France, Italy and the Netherlands, which led the foreign
investors in the amounted invested, accounted for 72 percent of
Poland's total capital influx.
</P>
<P>
Food processing, tobacco, finance and communications are the
favorite targets of investors. 
