to jointly fight drug trafficking along their common border, with
Myanmar pledging to frantically crack down amphetamine factories
located in the area.
</P>
<P>
Myanmar also agreed to Thailand's proposal to open three border
passes.
</P>
<P>
On repatriation of Myanmar refugees, Myanmar will set up a
committee to verify their nationalities before accepting them
back.
</P>
<P>
Regarding border demarcation, the two countries agreed to send
their technical teams to survey disputed area.  
