<HEADLINE> Michael Jordan to Resign with Bulls </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
WASHINGTON, August 27 (Xinhua) -- Michael Jordan, one of the
best players in the history of the National Basketball
Association, agreed Wednesday to resign with Chicago Bulls for
another season.
</P>
<P>
